<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The current docblock for Zend_Db_Table_Abstract::fetchRow() contains:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
* @return Zend_Db_Table_Row_Abstract|null The row results per the
*     Zend_Db_Adapter fetch mode, or null if no row found.
</code></pre>

<p>It would be better for auto-completion within IDEs (well, PDT at least) if it contained:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
* @return Zend_Db_Table_Row_Abstract (or null) The row results per the
*     Zend_Db_Adapter fetch mode, or null if no row found.
</code></pre>

<p>(or similar)</p>

